nodes.name: verifyProof
verifyProof

verifyProof(bytes32[],bytes32,bytes32).details: Verifies a Merkle proof proving the existence of a leaf in a Merkle tree. Assumes that each pair of leaves and each pair of pre-images are sorted.

params._proof: Merkle proof containing sibling hashes on the branch from the leaf to the root of the Merkle tree
